dataStructure.name: sid.org.tmforum.tip.service.spec.rfs.role.VPNTopologyServiceSpecRole
dataStructure.description:
This class defines the specific type of topology that is required to implement a particular CustomerFacingVPNService in terms of ResourceFacingServiceSpecRoles. Thus, it represents all of the invariant characteristics necessary to build a VPNTopologyService, abstracted in terms of ServiceSpecificationRoles. Please see the DEN-ng MPLS VPN model for more details.

This entity is optional
dataStructure.label: VPNTopologyServiceSpecRole
